---
---
<section id="conectar" class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center scroll-reveal">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-primary p-8 sm:p-12 lg:p-16 max-w-6xl mx-auto shadow-2xl shadow-primary/30">
      <!-- Decorative Background -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
        <svg width="100%" height="100%">
          <pattern id="cta-grid" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <circle cx="2" cy="2" r="1" fill="currentColor" class="text-white" />
          </pattern>
          <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#cta-grid)" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-gradient-radial from-secondary-300/30 to-transparent blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-gradient-radial from-primary-800/30 to-transparent blur-3xl"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-5">
          Pronta para <br class="hidden sm:block" />
          <span class="text-secondary-100">conhecer mulheres e viver mais?</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Baixe o app, entre em comunidades, converse com outras mulheres e comece a construir sua próxima experiência com mais confiança.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:gap-6">
          <a
            href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.viajadoras.app&pcampaignid=web_share"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-block transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <img
              src="/images/google-play-badge.svg"
              alt="Disponível no Google Play"
              class="w-36 sm:w-44 lg:w-auto lg:h-20 h-auto"
            />
          </a>

          <a
            href="https://apps.apple.com/br/app/viajadoras/id6755790482"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-block transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <img
              src="/images/app-store-badge.svg"
              alt="Baixar na App Store"
              class="w-36 sm:w-44 lg:w-auto lg:h-20 h-auto"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
